    versin, coversin, vercos, covercos
    aversin, acoversin, avercos, acovercos
    haversin, hacoversin, hacovercos
    ahaversin, hacoversin, havercos, ahacovercos
    exsec, aexsec, excsc, aexcsc
    crd, acrd
    epsilon

